casebody.data:
Tuesday, December 24, 1996

MOTION DOCKET

96-2258. State ex rel. Druggan v. Indus. Comm.

In Mandamus. On motion for peremptory or alternative writ, motion to expedite, and request for oral argument. Request for oral argument denied and alternative writ granted.

Moyer, C.J., Cook and Stratton, JJ., dissent and would dismiss the cause.
